{"data": [{"id": "4743451", "title": "Stitch Fix, Inc. 2025 Q1 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Stitch Fix, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q1 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106102\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743451-stitch-fix-inc-2025-q1-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 03:48:47"}, {"id": "4743442", "title": "Vail Resorts: Shares Are Worth Considering On Better Results, Higher Guidance", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A couple cross country skiing on a beautiful winter day.\" data-id=\"1661732562\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jordan Siemens</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>December 10th was a pretty decent day for shareholders of ski resort owner and operator <b>Vail Resorts, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MTN\" title=\"Vail Resorts, Inc.\">MTN</a></span>). Shares of the company rose by about 2.5% after management <a href=\"https://investors.vailresorts.com/news-releases/news-release-details/vail-resorts-reports-fiscal-2025-first-quarter-and-season-pass\" rel=\"nofollow\">announced</a>, the day before, financial results</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743442-vail-resorts-shares-are-worth-considering-on-better-results-higher-guidance", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 02:57:58"}, {"id": "4743440", "title": "Oracle Q2: Doubling CAPEX In FY 2025, Stock Remains A 'Sell'", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oracle Corporation\" data-id=\"1867844462\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Mesut Dogan</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I previously assigned a \u201cSell\u201d <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4720049-oracle-stock-q1-on-premise-offerings-concern0despite-oracle-databaseaws-launch-reiterate-sell\">rating</a> on <b>Oracle Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a></span>) in September 2024, highlighting their partnership with Amazon (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a>). Oracle delivered 9% revenue growth and 10% adjusted EPS growth for <a href=\"https://investor.oracle.com/investor-news/news-details/2024/Oracle-Announces-Fiscal-2025-Second-Quarter-Financial-Results/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Q2</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743440-oracle-q2-doubling-capex-in-fy25-stock-remains-a-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 02:33:07"}, {"id": "4743439", "title": "For ESGV, Ethics Is Not A Drag", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cityscape with sustainable building\" data-id=\"2152386308\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Eoneren/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>This article updates my </em><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4658996-esgv-ethical-etf-outperforming-in-2023\"><em>review of ESGV published one year ago</em></a><em>, in light of current portfolio and recent performance.</em></p> <h3><strong>ESGV strategy</strong></h3> <p>Vanguard ESG U.S. Stock ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">BATS:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ESGV\" title=\"Vanguard ESG U.S. Stock ETF\">ESGV</a></span>) was launched on 09/18/2018 and tracks the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152386308/image_2152386308.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743439-for-esgv-ethics-is-not-a-drag", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 02:17:51"}, {"id": "4743436", "title": "Pinterest Is A Strong Buy With GAAP Inflection Around The Corner", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Social Sharing Site Pinterest Prepares For Its IPO\" data-id=\"1141519003\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1045px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Justin Sullivan</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Pinterest (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PINS\" title=\"Pinterest, Inc.\">PINS</a></span>) is quickly becoming a \u201ccash cow\u201d but the market has not taken notice. Investors appear razor-focused on the potential for decelerating top-line growth as the company begins to lap tough comparables. Yet the company appears to be on the cusp of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743436-pinterest-is-a-strong-buy-with-gaap-inflection-around-the-corner", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 02:12:02"}, {"id": "4743435", "title": "Haleon: Guidance Implies Uncertainty Around Flu Season", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sensodyne Toothpaste Box in Hebrew\" data-id=\"477735211\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">verbaska_studio</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Haleon plc</b> (HLN, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HLNCF\" title=\"Haleon plc\">OTCPK:HLNCF</a>) had a good quarter, with strong pricing flex as well as volumes on average, albeit with some divergences across geographies. As in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4690042-haleon-stock-q1-earnings-pressures-are-temporary-but-closer-fair-value\">our previous coverage</a>, oral continues to be the most solid</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743435-haleon-guidance-implies-uncertainty-around-flu-season", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 02:08:57"}, {"id": "4743433", "title": "Nebius' Valuation Update After Backing From Nvidia", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Technologie m\u011bstsk\u00e9 s\u00edt\u011b v \u0160anghaji, \u010c\u00edna\" data-id=\"894977258\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Asia-Pacific Images Studio/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Last month we published an article on SA with our bullish thesis on <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4736928-nebius-group-well-positioned-to-be-ai-megatrend-winner\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4736928-nebius-group-well-positioned-to-be-ai-megatrend-winner\" target=\"_blank\">the Nebius Group N.V. (NASDAQ:</a><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NBIS\" title=\"Nebius Group N.V.\">NBIS</a></span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4736928-nebius-group-well-positioned-to-be-ai-megatrend-winner\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4736928-nebius-group-well-positioned-to-be-ai-megatrend-winner\" target=\"_blank\">).</a> In summary, we argued:</p> <ul> <li>Most money is made in global megatrends</li> <li>AI is the next global megatrend</li> <li>When selecting likely winners, focus on</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894977258/image_894977258.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743433-nebius-valuation-update-after-backing-from-nvidia", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 02:02:52"}, {"id": "4743432", "title": "The 2 Most Important Labor Market Sectors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Three workers (architects, engineers) examining building site\" data-id=\"1399023627\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Catherine Delahaye</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Analyzing the labor market is the most important component of the economy, since job losses are integral to the recessionary process.</p> <p>Not all sectors of the labor market are equally significant, and the biggest sectors are not necessarily</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399023627/image_1399023627.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743432-the-2-most-important-labor-market-sectors", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 01:52:55"}, {"id": "4743428", "title": "Ferroglobe: Poised To Exploit Silicon Boom But Poor Growth Limits Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty